parameters: Receptionist: Welcome, do you have an appointment?

future special police officer, I will investigate
this company.

Receptionist: If you don't have an appointment, I
can't let you in.

Receptionist: Even if you're a future special
police officer, please obtain proper permission
and come back again for the investigation.

\C[23]Rurika\C[0]: No problem, I will investigate here on my
own.

\C[23]Rurika\C[0]: I have destroyed the security of that
elevator.

Receptionist: ...Y-You're being really reckless,
aren't you?
Receptionist: Welcome, do you have an appointment?

Receptionist: We are currently closed for
business.

The button doesn't respond when pressed. It seems
that the security is activated.

Do you want to move to the midpoint of the SYSTEM
office?

Do you want to move to the deepest part of the
SYSTEM office?
